{"tid":713931,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都好想 自己老豆 變返做 自己細個嗰時嘅老豆？","createTime":"2018-06-23T08:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T21:00:06.000Z","uid":7109,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9ce0d24b698253f6c9c45ffbaa94df20aa042fda","tid":713931,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"唔係老豆變細個，而係變返自己仲係小朋友時嘅老豆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知幾時開始同老豆冇咩好講<br />\n係呢輪一齊睇世界盃先有啲嘢講下<br />\n基本上返到嚟佢就返房噤電話，再唔係就喺書枱寫嘢<br />\n<br />\n細個嗰時嘅老豆一返嚟就錫淡先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n週末就去踏單車，游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再唔係就喺屋企玩大富翁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對上一次同佢講生日快樂已經係六七年前<br />\n嗰次唔知做咩講完俾佢鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自此就冇再講<br />\n<br />\n真係好想細個嘅老豆返返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aecdf62339e1c81683158181aae568c335ec968","tid":713931,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:46:41.000Z","msg":"我相反"},{"pid":"f38e529ad7a51afc0d66c35cd01a891d0f93c395","tid":713931,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aecdf62339e1c81683158181aae568c335ec968","tid":713931,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:46:41.000Z","msg":"我相反"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"我細個同老母成日嘈，大個反而冇，依加好撚錫老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3a38e3bf840f986bdb7409019b66e951b69cfa","tid":713931,"uid":142358,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:48:24.000Z","msg":"唔撚想，細個老豆有燥狂症，做錯好小既事已經比佢打到仆街"},{"pid":"767f5fc05ec8e8e024a8ceaf1fee5c02cb3be1c2","tid":713931,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f38e529ad7a51afc0d66c35cd01a891d0f93c395","tid":713931,"uid":7109,"like":0,"di